## unihan-db 0.6.0 (2022-08-21)

### Internal

- Update unihan-etl 0.16.0 -> 0.17.2:

  - unihan-etl 0.16.0 adds `--no-cache` / `cache` as an option
  - unihan-etl 0.17.0 adds type annotations (`mypy --strict`)
